{"tid":297771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估國家】食到一半先發現 沙律附送原隻死青蛙","createTime":"2017-06-25T17:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T23:29:43.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"871dc534ae5b1b4f8dbaf039ad6d80881d77cd64","tid":297771,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:48:23.000Z","msg":"塞佩達(Shawna Cepeda)與家人到餐廳晚餐，她吃沙律時嚐了數口後覺得味道有點酸，「我看到有些東西捲起來」。她將異物交給丈夫並問他：「這是否生菜？」她的丈夫細心一看發現是青蛙。<br />\n<br />\n塞佩達向經理投訴&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;她又指餐廳其他沙律有機會受感染，其他食客亦有機會染病，但餐廳沒有作出預防措施，防止其他食客出現同類情況。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;事件已呈報給加州有關部門。"},{"pid":"1c1501fe6c4dd367e7e17570c781ab1d739e98c6","tid":297771,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498380677_f987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498380677_f987.jpg&h=81e8e17c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a739105f2b1e41b1cbba11cae4ebbb61a03632f","tid":297771,"uid":49392,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sphl3no9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsphl3no9&h=38a4a386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6944eec6900e3bc5855d7add4d747dda6e393b4","tid":297771,"uid":109573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/sphl3no9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsphl3no9&h=38a4a386&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7212708708453ae08fd8ca8e61d9a9320d9d2a","tid":297771,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n